Class UpperSFixedSeries

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.drip.function.gammaincomplete.UpperSFixedSeries
  • public class UpperSFixedSeries
extends java.lang.Object
    UpperSFixedSeries implements Upper Incomplete Gamma Expansion Series, starting with s = 0 if Recurrence is employed. The References are:

    • Gradshteyn, I. S., I. M. Ryzhik, Y. V. Geronimus, M. Y. Tseytlin, and A. Jeffrey (2015): Tables of Integrals, Series, and Products Academic Press
